## Import


An existing resource can be imported using its type token, name, and identifier, e.g.

```sh
$ pulumi import azure-nextgen:kubernetes:ConnectedCluster connectedCluster1 72f988bf-86f1-41af-91ab-2d7cd011db47 
```
